article.description: — Elijah Buchanan had 21 points on 9-of-12 shooting from the floor as Manhattan defeated Liberty 76-60 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Buchanan scores 21 to carry Manhattan past Liberty 76-60
article.linkText: Buchanan scores 21 to carry Manhattan past Liberty 76-60
article.story: KISSIMMEE, Fla. -- — Elijah Buchanan had 21 points on 9-of-12 shooting from the floor as Manhattan defeated Liberty 76-60 on Saturday night. Jose Perez had 14 points and seven assists for the Jaspers (4-1). Warren Williams added 13 points and Josh Roberts had seven rebounds. Keegan McDowell had 11 points for the Flames (1-3). Blake Preston added seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
